brokerageName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay
description: South End meets Southie! This stunning condo with a loft-like feel offers a rare opportunity to own in one of the best locations - Broadway T, Seaport, & Fort Point - are all in striking distance. Boasting an open layout with soaring 12ft ceilings, 10ft windows, exposed brick walls & ductwork plus sleek hardwood floors, this 2 bedroom/2 bathroom residence w/ one PARKING space, exudes a warm vibe with industrial touches. The upscale kitchen features tall custom cabinets/granite/stainless kitchen with a breakfast bar, & adjacent pantry is a chef's dream. A primary bedroom with en-suite bath & walk-in closet check off key boxes. Plus, a private balcony perfect for morning coffee or evening cocktails. This ELEVATOR & pet-friendly building features professional management, all next to the booming West Side.  Steps to Fox & The Knife, Amrheins, Worden Hall, many restaurants, shopping and the Broadway Red Line T.  Easy access to major routes & Logan Airport.
